}{\plain \fs24 \f2 \tab }{\plain \fs24 \b\f2 64.}{\plain \fs24 \f2   Virgil appears to Dante }{\plain \fs24 \b\f2 nel gran diserto}{\plain \fs24 \f2 .  The adjective is probably meant to recall \softline
the first description of the place, }{\plain \fs24 \i\f2 la piaggia diserta}{\plain \fs24 \f2  (}{\plain \fs24 \i\f2 Inf}{\plain \fs24 \f2 . I.29).\par
